ğŸ•’ Time & Space Complexity

Type	Complexity	Explanation

â° Time	O(N Ã— LÂ²)	N = number of words, L = word length (pattern generation + BFS)
ğŸ’¾ Space	O(N Ã— L)	For storing patterns and queue data
